      "description": "Step into a reliable and well-maintained vehicle that's ready for many more miles! This car is in good overall condition, showing just the expected minor signs of use while remaining mechanically sound and comfortable. It\u2019s been well-cared for and offers a great balance of performance and value for anyone looking for a dependable daily driver.",
