    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It\u2019s got a few minor signs of love here and there, but it runs like a dream and is ready for its next adventure! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
